row.question: Esteban is in a line at a theater. If he is the 26th person counting from the back of the line and the 18th person counting from the front of the line, how many people are in the line?
row.rationale:
Total no. of persons = (Position of A from left + Position of A from right) -1
Total no. of persons = (26 + 18) – 1 = 44 – 1 = 43
Ans C
